  "subject": "Create Loop from the available Loop templates.",
  "commit_message": "Create Loop from the available Loop templates.\n\nUI and Backend changes to support creation of Control Loop using a Loop Template.\n\nConfiguration Policy moodal to support a Dropdown for choosing the Policy variant if a Microservice(loop element model) has more than one associated Policy models.\nDropdown uses the acronym field to display as label and value as policy model type.\n\nRead Only flags to control certain actions based on users permissions\n\nIssue-ID: CLAMP-587\nSigned-off-by: Ashwin Sharma <ashwin.shyam.sharma@att.com>\nChange-Id: Ic594cbe512204b472dc3b0fb83a5558adefdb9ad\n",
